          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Extra Points -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Go fast and hit the jump, your bike should clear.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Power Up -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Circle + Triangle + Square + X when in danger.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; New Life -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Press keys to just jump over track by pressing X + R2 + Z and you have unlocked an extra play.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Level Jump -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Press L1 + Square in beginning of second race.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
